# The root .gitignore blanket-ignores *.html (scraped research-scratch HTML).
# This paper's HTML is authored SOURCE, not scratch — re-include it here.
!paper.html
!sections/
!sections/*.html

# Chrome-render QA scratch (regenerable screenshots)
_qa_*.png

# Appendix figure-source: track the durable sources + renders, ignore local render
# tooling (the headless-Chrome screenshot audit, the puppeteer config, node_modules).
figs_src/_audit/
figs_src/_audit_render.py
figs_src/pup.json
figs_src/node_modules/
# the root .gitignore blanket-ignores *.html; re-include the figs_src sources we DO track
!figs_src/*.mmd
!figs_src/*.py
!figs_src/*.png
!figs_src/README.md
# …but NOT the local render tooling: the `!figs_src/*.py` line above re-includes
# every .py, so re-exclude the audit-render script HERE (a later pattern wins) —
# otherwise the line-13 ignore is silently overridden and the scratch tracks.
figs_src/_audit_render.py
